{"pr_pilot":{"received_at":"2026-04-28T06:24:06Z","event_type":"pull_request","action":"edited","category":"info"},"payload":{"action":"edited","number":2727,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/2727","id":3594001429,"node_id":"PR_kwDORzg8fM7WOBwV","html_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2727","diff_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2727.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2727.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/issues/2727","number":2727,"state":"open","locked":false,"title":"perf: optimize Arrow JSON serialization hot path","user":{"login":"strawgate","id":6384545,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYzODQ1NDU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6384545?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate","html_url":"https://github.com/strawgate","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"Adds a batch-level JSON serialization path with buffer pre-reservation and reworks the inner string escape scan with 8-byte SWAR processing, a no-escape fast path, and a manual hex table for control character escaping.\n\n- Add `write_batch_json_resolved` for batch-level serialization with pre-reserved buffers\n- Replace per-row loops in `JsonLinesSink` and `StdoutSink` with single `write_batch_json_resolved` calls\n- Accelerate `first_escape_pos` with SWAR bit tricks (8\u00d7 faster on typical log data)\n- Add fast path in `write_json_string` that avoids allocation when no escaping is needed\n- Replace `format_args!` for control character escaping with a static hex table and `extend_from_slice`\n\n<!-- Macroscope's pull request summary starts here -->\n<!-- Macroscope will only edit the content between these invisible markers, and the markers themselves will not be visible in the GitHub rendered markdown. -->\n<!-- If you delete either of the start / end markers from your PR's description, Macroscope will append its summary at the bottom of the description. -->\n> [!NOTE]\n> ### Optimize Arrow JSON serialization by introducing `write_batch_json_resolved` batch writer\n> - Adds `write_batch_json_resolved` in [`row_json.rs`](https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2727/files#diff-9f738244fd6e9e022e6de11f78d320f4377015d04bbb4103883cba4b8cb8f67f) to serialize a full Arrow batch as NDJSON in one call using pre-resolved column infos, replacing per-row loops in both [`json_lines.rs`](https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2727/files#diff-fffa8ebe0f0429fe00b321b04d3a64b7dcc5a19dac1cb7d625a847e3ba34c93c) and [`stdout.rs`](https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2727/files#diff-72bfe4536b55bfc85db387849ce200ae4846904237c13d91e8838f7a203b9faf).\n> - Reworks the JSON string escaping path to avoid `format_args!` and `write_fmt`: a fast path skips escaping entirely when no special characters are present, and control characters are hex-encoded by writing digits directly.\n> - Pre-reserves output buffer capacity using a heuristic based on column count to reduce allocations per batch.\n> - Adds a `write_batch_json_resolved` benchmark case to [`json_lines.rs`](https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2727/files#diff-69b195325798b5e628e6732d232b1f0770240d6c034dd1b8a78496f3326647ec) for measuring the new hot path.\n>\n